Question: Jilin Yongli Laser Technology Co., Ltd. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Jilin Yongli Laser Technology Co., Ltd.

Product: CO2 Laser Tubes

- CO2 laser tubes ranging from 25W to 300W
- Products approved by ISO9001:2015, CE, FCC, FDA, REACH, and ROHS
- Annual production capacity of 60,000 pieces
- R&D center established in 2007 with strong technical strength
- Products independently developed with over 50 national authorized patents
- Exported to 88 countries, trademark registered in 50 countries
- Unique producing techniques for stable working status
- A4s and H4 laser tubes suitable for cutting and engraving applications
- A4s series combines latest technologies and top-notch raw materials
- H series developed for cost-effective cutting and engraving results
